message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.IR", "cs.AI", "cs.DB", and "cs.LG". This is because the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) techniques for answering complex questions, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG).
